screen_name: Then a week after that I got sick last Thursday and my fever didn’t break till like Sunday night. Now we just gotta see about my mom and dad.
So I’ve had fever for the past like 3 days. I honestly don’t know if it’s COVID or not, but all I know is that this thing sucks.

So first before we got into quarantine my little brother was complaining about a girl in his class being sick. Then he ended up getting sick with a high fever, but at the time there weren’t enough tests to test him. Then about two weeks later my little sister gets sick.
So my COVID-19 test results came back and I tested positive for COVID-19. I’ve already recovered but I need to see about by parents, especially my dad. When I get a chance I want to donate plasma.
